Package de.mrapp.android.adapter.datastructure

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DataStructure
    Defines the interface, all classes, which represent a data structure, must implement.
    Parameterizable
    Defines the interface, all classes, which should allow to store key value pairs, must implement.
    Restorable
    Defines the interface, a class whose state should be able to be stored, before an activity is killed and restored after it has been reinitialized, must implement.
    Unmodifiable
    A data structure, which implements this interface, indicates that it is restricted to read-only accesses.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractAdapterItem<DataType>
    An abstract base class for all data structure, which holds the data of an item of an adapter.
    AbstractUnmodifiableList<DataType,EncapsulatedType>
    An abstract base class for all implementations of the type List, which should throw exceptions of the type UnsupportedOperationException when attempted to be modified.
    AppliedFilter<DataType>
    A representation of a filter, which has been applied on an adapter's underlying data.
    UnmodifiableList<Type>
    An implementation of the type List, which throws exceptions of the type UnsupportedOperationException when attempted to be modified.
